Shillong, Jymmang 10: Ka Khasi Hills Autonomous District Council (KHADC) kaba dei ban sumar bad ïada ïa ki khlaw ki btap kat kum ka hukum jong ka Ïingkashari Supreme Court, kala leh matlah ïa ka jingpom dieng pathar ha ki khlaw ka Ri-Bhoi District kham tam ha ki thaiñ Byrwa kaba la kylla long mynta kum ka Kad khaïi dieng be-aiñ.

Shaei ka Working Plan Working Scheme jong ka Ïingkashari Supreme Court?..Hato ka KHADC ka la don ïa ka Working Scheme ba lah ban ai jingbit ïa ka jingpom dieng hapoh u pud u sam jong ka, la ka dei ka khlaw Hima, khlaw Raid, Khlaw Shnong ne wat ki khlaw shimet.

Ki Khlaw ba rben ha shilynter ka surok na Lad Sumer sha Zero Point ba kynthup ïa ka Byrwa, 4 Nombor, 5 Nombor, Umtham, Ryngkang Khla bad ki Sshnong ba marjan khamtam ki khlaw ba don harud jong ka Wah 5 Nombor, kila syllen lut mynta na ka jingpom dieng pathar bad kaba ipang met ban peit ka long ba baroh ki dieng met (ki jait pa ki jait dieng) kila shah pom lut naduh kiba rit eh haduh kiba heh na ka jingrhah jubor jong ki Nongkhaïi dieng.

Kaba isangsot eh ka long ym tang ka jingpom ïa ki dieng kala pynsyllen lut ïa ki khlaw hynrei wat ka Wah Umtrew kaba tuid sha Dam Zero Point kala jot la julor na ka jingpynkhyllem ïa ki dieng hapoh Wah, kaba long kum ka jingdusmon ïa ki dohkha dohpnat kiba im ha kane ka Wah.

Ka Shnong Byrwa kala kylla mynta kum ka Kad Khaïi Dieng bad baroh ki dieng ba pom na ki khlaw jong ka thaiñ la lum thup ha kane ka Shnong ban pynïaid iew sha ki karkhana bad ki Pajwa thang mawshun kiba don ha kylleng ki jaka ka Jylla.

Lah ban kdew hangne ba ka Working Plan Working Scheme ka dei kaba hap ban pynkhreh da ka Jylla (Sorkar bad ADC) kat kum ka jingbthah jong ka Ïingkashari Supreme Court haba pynjynsur ïa ka hukum khang pomdieng ha Jylla ba la pynjari ha u snem 1996. Ïa ka Working Plan Working Sheme hap ban mynjur da ka Ministry of Environment & Forest (MOEF) ka Sorkar Kmie.

Ka KHADC kaba don ïala ka jong ka Tnad Khlaw kaba dei ban ïada bad sumar ïa ki khlaw ki btap, kala leh matlah ïa kane ka jing pom dieng pathar ha kane ka thaiñ jong ka Ri-Bhoi kaba hap hapoh ka Umsning Constituency....Shaei ka “The United Khasi Jaintia Hills Autonomous District (Management and. Control of Forest) Act. 1958 bad ka ‘The UK-JHAD (Management and Control of Forests) Rules, 1960..’...Hato kane ka Aiñ ka dei thik tang na ka bynta ban buh Check Gate ban ïoh kamai khajna na ki dieng ne ki markhlaw?.

Ka KHADC ka dei ban buh jingkylli ïa ki Heh Ophisar ka Tnad Forest khamtam ïa u Forest Ranger ba dei khmih ïa kane ka thaiñ- balei ba matlah ïa kane ka jingpom dieng pathar kaba long kum ka jingpynkheiñ ïa ka hukum jong ka Ïingkashari Supreme Court kaba la buh da ki kyndon ban hap bud thik pa thik la ka long ïa ka Sorkar Jylla ne ki Autonomous District Council (ADC).

“Ka jingpom dieng hapoh u pud u sam ka Sixth Schedule ka dei ka jingkhmih bad jingkitkhlieh jong ki District Council. Ki Council kim lah ban shu ai jingbit pomdieng pathar khlem ka Working Scheme” ong u CP Marak, Principal Chief Conservator of Forest (PCCF) ka Sorkar Jylla haba bynrap “Ka Tnad Khlaw jong ka Jylla kam lah ban tuklar ïa u pud u sam ka Sixth Schedule”.

Une u Heh Ophisar u ong ba kumba long mynta ka KHADC kam pat don satia la ka jong ka Working Scheme bad ka jingpom ïa ki dieng ka long kaba be-aiñ lada ym ïoh jingbit kat kum ka scheme ne ki Rules pom dieng.

Haba kubur ba ka jingpom dieng ha ki thaiñ Byrwa-Umtham ka long kaba be-aiñ, u Additional Chief Forest Officer (ACFO) ka KHADC Bah R.Kylla ula ong “Haduh mynta hi ngi khlem ai jingbit ban pom dieng na ki khlaw jong ka thaiñ bad ka Ophis kam don jingtip ruh ïa ka jingpom dieng. Ngi khlem pat ïoh ïa kano kano ka report kynthup ka report na u Ranger ba dei ban peit ïa ka Range”.

U Bah Kylla u ong ba lada ka Ophis ka ïoh ïa ka report, kan sa phah tohkit bad sa leh ïa kaba donkam.

Kum ban shu pynkynmaw, ka Executive Committee jong ka People’s Democratic Forum (PDF) ba synshar ïa ka KHADC ha ka Dorbar synai jong u snem bala lah, kala wanrah ïa artylli ki Bill-ka United Khasi-Jaintia Hills Autonomous District (Management and Control of Forest) (VIth Amendment) Bill, 2016 bad Amendment Rules, 2016 lem bad ka United Khasi-Jaintia Hills District Fisheries Act (Second Amendment) Bill, 2016. da ka jingthmu ban ïada bad sumar ïa ki khlaw ki btap bad ki jingim ba don ha ki Wah kiba hap hapoh u pud u sam ka KHADC.

Haduh katno kine ki Bill ka KHADC ki lah ban wanrah jingmyntoi bad long shisha ki lad jingïada naba wat ïa ki Aiñ bala don lypa bad khamtam eh ka hukum jong ka Ïingkashari Supreme Court ruh ym shym la lah ban pyntreikam. Shillong, Jymmang, 10: Ki nongri Khñiang kiba trei kum ki Muster Roll ha ka tnat Sericulture & Weaving ka Sorkar Jylla ki la pan jingpynshai na ki bor bahalor hadien ba ki la lap ïa ki kyrteng jong ki ‘Nongtrei Rngai’ na ka jubab RTI ba la pan da ka Kong Angela Rngad na kane ka tnat.

Ka Thma u Rangli Juki (TUR) ka la rai ban leit mudui sha u Vigilant Commisioner ka Jylla da kaba aiti ïa ka kaiphod ba la lap na ka jubab RTI ba la ïoh na ka tnat Sericulture and Weaving. Ha kajuh ka Kong Angela Rngad ka la kyntu ïa ki Ophisar bad ïa ki bor pynïaid kane ka tnat ba kim dei ban wengkam ne byrngem ïa ki Muster Roll ba mih shakhmat ban long ki sakhi halor kane ka jubab RTI namar ki dawa ban ïoh ïa ka jingpynshai halor ka jingshah wengkam bad ka jingshah pyndonkam bakla ïa ki kyrteng Rngai ba la pynrung ha ki Muster Roll Sheet.

Da ki phew ngut ki nongtrei Muster Roll ka tnat Sericulture and Weaving na Ri-Bhoi, East Khasi Hills bad Ummulong mynta ka sngi ki la wan ïashim bynta ha ka Public Hearing ba la pynlong da ka Thma u Rangli Juki, (TUR) ha Deba Das Memorial Community Hall, Bishnupur, Shillong, ha ryngkat ka jingïadonlang u Pastor Nathan Diengdoh bad i Kong Patricia Mukhim, Editor ka kotkhubor The Shillongtimes kiba long kum ki Nongpeit Pyrman kynthup.

Katkum ka jubab RTI la lap naduh u snem 2010 haduh 2016, la lap ba la siew tulop pynban sha ki“Nongtrei Rngai” kiba la pynrung da ki Manager ba dei khmih ïa kine ki Farm bad lap ruh ba ki don ki Muster Roll kiba la shah soi tuh ka kyrteng ha ki bnai ba ki la shah pynsangeh jingtrei ha kane ka tnat.

I Kong E. Kharkongor, Muster Roll ka Govt. Sericulture Reeling Unit, East Khasi Hills District i la pynpaw ïa ka jingsngew lyngngoh ban lap na ka thup soi kyrteng jong ka Muster Roll Sheet kaba pynpaw ba ki don haduh 15 ngut ki nongtrei katba ha ka jingshisha ki Muster Roll ba ju trei manla ka sngi ki don tang 10 ngut kiba ju ïoh ka jingsiewdor sngi kaba T.140 spah.

Haba kheiñ ïa ka jingpisa ba la pynsyrwa ban siew sha ki Nongtrei Rngai kiba paw kyrteng ha ka Muster Roll Sheet naduh u snem 2010 haduh 2015 ka long T.5,71,560 lak.

“Nga lyngngoh ban ïohi na ka jubab RTI ba la sei pisa ha ka kyrteng jong nga wat hadien ba nga la shah pynsangeh treikam naduh Ïaiong, 3013 haduh April 2014,” la ong i Kong K. Kharkongor, i para jong i Kong E. Kharkongor.

“Shano ka pisa ka leit bad kito kiba donkti halor kane, ki dei ban ai jingpynshai,” ong i Kong E Kharkongor.

I Kong J. War, ba trei Muster Roll ha ka jaka ri Khñiang (Regional Farm) ka tnat Sericulture ha Ummulong, i la ong, “wat ïa ka tulop ruh ngi ïoh ha Kper. Kim (Manager) ju khot ïa ngi ban soi ïa ka Muster Roll Sheet hynrei ki shu phah soi beit tang ïa ka Stamp namar ngim ju leit hi ruh ha ophis ki Manager.”

U Bah Ambrose Rymbai, Kurim jong i Kong J. War, u pynpaw ka jingkyndit ban ïoh ïa kyrteng jong u kaba paw ha ka Muster Roll Sheet wat hadien ba u la shah pynpep trei naduh 2014 haduh 2016.

“Kumno ki pyndonkam ban soi thok ïa ka kyrteng jong nga,” ong u Bah Ambrose bad bynrap, “wat haba nga khlem trei shuh.”

Nalorkata, i Kong J. War i ïathuh ba ki nongtrei Muster Roll ha Regional Farm, Ummulong ki don tang 7 ngut hynrei katba ki “Nongtrei Rngai” ba paw kyrteng ha ka Muster Roll Sheet ki don jin haduh 24 ngut ha kaba la pyni ba la siew T.140 spah shi sngi.

Haba kynthoh halor ka jingpynduna bai sngi da ka tnat Sericulture and Weaving, kane ka longkmie ka la ong, “nalor ba ki siew tang T. 100 ha ka shisngi ym T.140 kumba pynpaw ha ka Muster Roll Sheet hynrei wat haba ngi pep trei tang shi sngi ruh ki khate noh ïa ka bainong sngi jong ngi.”

I Kong P. Lyngdoh Khatar, Muster Roll ka Sericulture Nongpoh i ïathuh, ha u snem 2010-2015 ki don tang 10 ngut kiba trei Muster Roll bad ha u snem 2017 ki don sa tang 7 ngut. Hynrei katkum ka jubab RTI la lap ba ki Nongtrei Rngai ki don haduh 58 ngut.

I ïathuh ruh ha u snem 2015 ki don 15 ngut ki Muster Roll kiba la shah pynpep trei hynrei kaba lyngngoh pat ka long ba ki kyrteng ki dang paw ha ka Muster Roll Sheet.

Haba ïathuh halor ka jingïoh jingsiew, i la ong, “naduh u snem 2010 ngi ïoh tang 160 tyngka shisngi haduh u snem 2015 watla ka dor sngi ka dei T.180 shi sngi. Hynrei ha ka Muster Roll Sheet la pynpaw ba la siew T.180 shi sngi, katba kiba ïoh ïa ka jingsiew T.180 shi sngi ki don tang arngut.” I ïathuh bynniaw ruh ba ka tnat Sericulture ka khate beit ïa ka bai sngi wat lada ki pep trei tang shi sngi haba ki pang ne shitom.

Ym tang katta, ka tnat Sericulture ka la pynrung ruh ïa ka kyrteng ki khun jong ki Muster Roll ha ka Muster Roll kum ki Nongtrei Rngai bad pynpaw thik thik ruh ba ïa ka bai sngi kaba ju siew shi bnai kynthih la siew sha ka Personal Account jong ki.

La lap ruh lyngba ka jubab RTI ba ka Laxmi Rai, kaba la trei naduh u snem 1963 ha Reeling Unit ka la shah sangeh noh kynsan na ka kam Muster Roll ha u bnai Risaw, 2015, katba ka kyrteng ka dang paw ha ka Muster Roll Sheet ba pyni ba ka jingsiew bai sngi ka dang bteng haduh 2016.

Kane ka jubab RTI ba la sei madan mynta ka sngi ka la pynsawkyrang ïa u C.K Marak, Deputy Director bad ïa ki ophisar ka tnat Sericulture and Weaving kiba la ïadonlang ha kane ka Public Hearing hadien ba kine ki Muster Roll ki la pynpaw paidbah ïa ka jingshah pyndonkam bakla ka kyrteng, ka jingsoi kaba pynpaw pyrthei ïa ka jyrsieh bamsap bashyrkhei kaba hapoh kane ka tnat.

U C. K. Marak um shym la lah satia ban ai jubab ba pynhun ïa kine ki Muster Roll halor kane ka jubab RTI wat na ka liang ka Kong R Lyngwa, DSO ka Ribhoi ka la jubab kulmar haba pan jingpynshai halor ka jingpynmih ka tnat Sericulture ïa ka kyrteng ki “Nongtrei Rngai” ha ka Muster Roll Sheet bad ka jingpyndonkam bakla ïa ka kyrteng ki Khun jong ki.

Ka Kong Angela Rngad ka la ong, “haba bishar katkum ka jubab RTI ngi lap ba ka don ka jyrsieh bamsap kaba shyrkhei bha na ka jingsiew bainong ïa ki Muster.” Shillong, Jymmang 10 : Ka Khasi Hills Autonomous District Council (KHADC) ka la pynkhreh mynta ban ïa khun pyrshah ïa ka hukum ba pynmih da ka Meghalaya High Court ban pynpyntreikam ïa ka Limitation Act, 1963 ha kane ka jylla.

“Shen ngin sa rai, la ngin ujor da ka Review Petition ha ka High Court lane da ka Special Leave Petition (SLP) shah ka Supreme Court pyrshah ïa katei ka hukum,” ong u Chief Executive Member ka KHADC, Bah PN Syiem haba kren bad ki lad pathai khubor hadien ka jingïakynduh ïa ki dkhot ka HNYF hynne ka sngi.

Katkum ka jingong jong u CEM, katei ka aiñ ka lah ban ktah haduh katta katta ïaka hok jong ki trai muluk trai jaka ha kiba bun ki bynta. La ong ruh ba katkum katei ka Limitation Act, 1963, kito kiba kwah ban ujor pyrshah ïa kano kano ka hukum ki hap ban leh ïa kata ha ito i por ba la buh ne kdew lym kumta kin ym ïoh lad shuh.

Na ka liang u Bah PN Syiem u la ïathuh ruh ba ha kane ka taïew hi un lum ïa ki stad aiñ ban ïa kren bad ïatai sani halor katei ka bynta. Ïa katei ka sienjam u CEM u la pynpaw hadien ba ka HNYF hapoh ka jingïalam jong u General Secretary, Bah Sadon Blah, ki la kyrpad ïa ka KHADC ba kadei ban tuklar mardor halor katei ka phang.

Da kaba kdew halor ka hukum ba pynmih da ka Meghalaya High Court ha ka 12tarik Ïaiong, 2017, u Bah Sadon u la ong ruh ba katei ka aiñ kan ktah ruh wat ïa ka Khyrnit ba Hynriew jong ka Riti Synshar jong ka Ri bad wat ïa ka rukom treikam jong ki district council.

Na ka liang u Bah Sadon haba kren bad ki lad pathai khubor ula ong ba ïa katei ka hukum lada ym lah ban shimkhia ha ka lynti kaba dei bad ha ka por kaba biang, kan ktah wat ïa ki kamram treikam jong ki Autonomous District Council ha ka jylla.

Nalorkata, u la ong ruh ba lada ïa ka aiñ (Act) jong ka Parliament la pyntreikam khlem da bishar bniah shwa ïa ki kyndon jong ka Sixth Schedule, kam don jingmut shuh ban don wat ïa ki district council.

Na ka liang utei u heh ka HNYF u la ong ruh ba ha ka 22tarik u Jymmang, 1989 u Secretary jong ka tnad Law ka sorkar Meghalaya u la kdew shai ha ka shithi sha u Regional Manager -II ka State Bank of India (Regional Office), Dhanketi ba ka Limitation Act, 1963 kam treikam shuh ha ki jaka riewlum jong kane ka jylla.

Ha katei ka jingiakynduh, ia ka HNYF la synran lang ruh da u Executive Member ka tnad Elaka Bah Latiplang Kharkongor bad MDC ka Laban, Bah Ricky Shullai. Shillong, Jymmang 10: Ka Jaiñtia Hills Autonomous District Council (JHADC) ka dei ka Council ba nyngkong eh napdeng ki lai tylli ki Autonomous District Council (ADC) ka Jylla, kaba la jam shakhmat ban shim ïa ki lad ban ïada bad sumar ïa ki khlaw ki btap kumba la bthah da ka Ïingkashari Supreme Court hadien ba pynjynsur ïa ka hukum khang pomding u snem 1996.

Ka Khasi Hills Autonomous District Council (KHADC) ka dei kaba shatdong eh bad kat haduh mynta kam pat leh eiei satia watla ki khlaw ki btap kila nang syllen nang syllen wat hapdeng ki aiñ ki kanun ba kala thaw.

Kane ka jingïapher kala paw na ka jingpyntreikam ïa ka Working Plan bad Working Scheme bala bthah da ka Ïingkashari Supreme Court-kaba khang ban pom dieng khlem da don ka scheme ban pynjyrngam bujli ïa ki jaka.

Kat kum ka khubor na ka Tnad Forest & Environment ka Jylla, ka JHADC haduh mynta kala pyntreikam ïa artylli ki Working Scheme bad ha ka bynta kaba ar, kane ka Council kala pynkhreh haduh 56 tylli ki Skhim ban lah pomdieng hapoh ka District kat kum ka jingdonkam. Hynrei ka KHADC haduh mynta kam pat don satia wat kawei ruh ka Working Scheme kaba la treikam hapoh u pud u sam jong ka.

“Ka JHADC mynta kala pynkhreh haduh 56 tylli ki Working Scheme ki ban sa ïoh jingmynjur mynta na ka MoEF” ong u CP Marak Principal Chief Conservator of Forest (PCCF) ka Jylla haba bynrap “Kane ka Council kala dep pyntrei teng ïa ki Working Scheme ha ki snem bala leit”.

Hynrei haba phai sha ka KHADC, une u Heh Ophisar ula ong “Ka KHADC kala ïoh teng ïa kawei ka Working Scheme ha ki snem bala leit hynrei ka khlem lah satia ban pyntreikam pura ïa ka. Mynta lei kam shym la don satia kano kano ka jingtyrwa working Scheme na ka Council”.

U CP Marka u ïathuh ba dang myn ha ka 18 tarik Ïaiong, u Addl PCCF ula lum ïa ka jingïalang bad baroh ki Chief Forest Officer jong ki lai Tylli ki Autonomous District ban ïasyllok halor ka jingpynkhreh ïa ki Working Scheme hynrei na ka liang ka KHADC kala pyni jingeh ba kam lah satia ban pynkhreh ïa ka jingtyrwa.

Halor kane, u ïathuh ba ka Tnad kala kyntu ïa ka JHADC kaba la pyntrei shaid shaid ïa ka Working Scheme ba kan iarap lem ïa ka KHADC ha kaban shna ïa ka Scheme khnang ba kan long ka lad jingïada ïa ka mariang. Nongpoh, Jymmang 10 : Wat la shibun ki jingeh ba ki nongrep Slasha ha Ri Bhoi ki ïa kynduh jingeh ban kyntiew ïa ka kam rep Slasha kaba ki angnud mynta ban pynmih ïa ki Slasha ba khlem da ai dawai (Organic Tea), hynrei ka jingiaineh bad ka jinglen lade ban kyntiew ïa kane ka kam rep Slasha ka la sdang ban seisoh bad daw ïaid shaphrang kumba la angnud da ki Nongrep Sla ka Ri Bhoi.

Kane ka la paw pyrthei mynta ka sngi ha Ri Bhoi, ha kaba u Myntri Rangbah ka jylla, u Dr. Mukul Sangma ha ka jingdon ryngkat u Myntri barim ka jylla, u Dr. Mukul Sangma ula wan ban buh ïa u Mawnongrim jong ka Karkhana Shna Sla ba la tip ha ka ktien Nongwei kum ka Tea Processing Unit, kaba dei kawei na ka Karkhana kaba kin pynmih ïa u Slasha ba khlem da ai dawai.

La sakhi lang ruh ha kane ka sngi ba la plie ïa u Mawnongrim katei ka Karkhana Shna Slasha da ka jingdon lang u P. Sampath Kumar, IAS, Commissioner & Secretary, Agriculture, u Assistant Director Agriculture, u Bah Maqbool Lyngdoh Suiam, u Deputy Commissioner ka Ri Bhoi, CP Gothmare, u Superintendent of Police, u R.P Singh bad kynthup ruh kiwei kiwei ki riew rangbah, ki nongrep slsha bad ki dkhot nongïalam ka ARSLA Tea Grower’s and Producers Society.

U Bah Comfortstone Rympei bad u Bah B.W Chyne, uba dei u Secretary ka Society, ha kane ka jingwan buh ïa u mawnongrim da u Myntri Rangbah ka jylla, ki la ai ruh ka jingkren ban pynshai sha ki paidbah halor ka jingiaid lynti halor ka kam rep slasha ha Ri Bhoi, kaba ki ïa kynduh jingeh bad kumno ki poi shaduh katei ka thong kaba ki angnud ban kyntiew ïa ka rep slasha kaba khlem da pyndonkam ïa ki dawai dashin (fertilizer).

U Bah B.M Chyne, u la ïathuh ruh ba ka kam rep slasha ha Ri Bhoi ka la sdang mynta la 30 snem ha Ri Bhoi bad ka jingeh kaba ki ïa kynduh ka dei ka jingbym don la ka jong ka Karkhana ban shna slasha ha kaba ïa ki slasha ba ki kheit na ki Kper slasha la hap ban die tad sha Assam.

U la ïathuh ruh ha kaba sdang ka sorkar ka la pyrshang ban ai ka jingkyrshan ïa ki nongrep slasha ban kyntiew ïa ka kam rep slasha kum ka lad ïoh kam ioh jam ban pyndap ïa ka ïing ka sem, hynrei kane ka jingiarap ka sorkar kala kut noh tang ha shiteng lynti bad bun nongrep slsha ki la ban sangeh noh namar kim lah ban kot bor halor ka jinglut jingsep kaba ki donkam ban kyntiew ïa ka kam rep slasha.

U la ïathuh ruh ba ïa ka Arsla Organic Tea Growers and Producers Cooperative Society la sui la shor ïa ka bad la register ruh sha ka sorkar da ka jingthmu ba ki ïakhun ban don noh la ka jong kata ka Karkhana ban shna Slasha, khnang ba kin lah ban kyrshan ïa ka kam rep slasha bad kumjuh ruh kan long ka jingmyntoi ha ka liang ka kamai ka kajih lyngba ka kam rep slasha ban pyndap ïa ka ïing ka sem.

Shuh shuh, u la ong ruh don shibun ki jingeh ba kum ki nongrep slasha ki ïa kynduh ha ka kam rep slasha, hynrei da ka jingkyrshan bad ka jingkitkhlieh ka Tea Development Centre, Umsning, ka la don shibun ka jingkylla bad ki la ioh ruh shibun ki jingmyntoi ban dang kyntiew ïa ka kam rep slasha. Kum ka Society ka khmih lynti ruh ba ka sorkar kan dang kyrshan ïa ki nongrep slasha ha ka jylla khnang ba ka jingthmu bad ka jingangnud ban kyntiew ïa ka kam rep slasha kan long kaba jop bad ruh ki nongrep slasha kin ioh ïa ka jingmyntoi ban pyndap ïa ka ïing ka sem lyngba ka kam rep slasha, u la bynrap.

Haba kren ruh ha kane ka sngi kum u kongsan ban plie ïa utei u Mawnongrim ka Tea Processing Unit ha Umsning, u Dr. Mukul Sangma u la ai ka jingiaroh kaba khraw ïa ki nongrep slasha ka Ri Bhoi, namar wat hapdeng shibun ki diengpyngkiang bad ki jingduna ba ki ïa kynduh ha ka kam rep slasha, hynrei ki kloi ban iaineh bad ruh ban pynim ïa kane ka kam rep slasha ha ka jylla.

U la ong ruh ba na ka liang ka sorkar ruh ka la pynshlur ïa ki nongrep ba kin shim ïa ka kam rep kaba khlem da pyndonkam dawai, namar ka thong jong ka sorkar ka longba ki paidbah kin lait ban bam ïa ki jhur ki jhep ne ki jingthung kiba la wieh dawai kaba lah ban ktah ïa ka koit ka khiah ki paidbah.

Kumba ka Society ka la kyrpad ruh ïa u Myntri ba un phai khmat sha ki nongrep Slasha, u Dr. Mukul u la ong ba ki nongrep slasha ki dei ban don ka jingiatylli bad ka jingtrei shitom ban kyntiew ïa kane ka kam rep slasha, anmar ka kam rep slasha kam dei tang kata ka kam kaba ki lah ban kyrshan ïa ka ïing ka sem, hynrei lada ngi lah ban pynheh shuh shuh ïa ka jaka rep slasha kan long ruh kum kawei na ka jaka jngohkai pyrthei ban khring ïa ki nongjngohkai ba na shabar jong ka jylla.

U la ruh ba ka sorkar kan bteng ban ai ka jingkyrshan ïa ki nongrep slasha ha ka jylla bad u la kyntu ruh ïa ka Society ba kan jied ïa ka jaka kaba kham heh ban pynlong kum kawei na ka jaka jngohkai pyrthei lyngba ka kper slasha, namar ka thong jong ka sorkar ka kwah ban kyntiew ïa ki nongrep ym tangba ki ïoh jingmyntoi na ka jingmih jong u slasha hynrei kin ioh jingmyntoi ruh na ki nongjngohkai pyrthei ba na shabar ka jylla ban kyntiew ïa ka ioh ka kot jongki.

Nalor ba u la kular ba ka sorkar kan shim khia ban iarap ïa ki nongrep slasha ha ka jylla, u Dr. Mukul Sangma, u la kyntu ruh ïa ki nongrep slasha ba kin pynmih ïa ki slasha kiba iaid ïew (Good Quality), khnang ba u slasha uba mih na ka jylla un iaid ïew ym tang ha ka jylla, hynrei un iaid iew ruh wat shabar ka jylla bad ka ri kaba long shisha ka jingmyntoi ban kyntiew ïa ka ioh ka kot jong ki paidbah lyngba ka kam rep slasha ha ka jylla, u la bynrap.

