Haba phai sha jingjop ka DSK Shivajians, ka BFC ka dei kawei na ki team kaba baroh ki kyrmen ba kan ioh rah ïa ka nam lahduh kane ka lympung khamtam ruh ba ka dei ka klob ïalehkai phutbol ba radbah ha ka ri. Ïa kitei ki arkol ka Shivajians la thep da u Juan Quero lyngba ka penalty ha ka minit kaba 71 bad ka free-kick ha ka ka minit kaba 76').

Ha kane ka jingïakhun hynne ka sngi ka DSK Shivajians ka la sei madan haduh hynriew ngut ki player U-22. Ka khubor kaba kmen eh ka dei na ka jingioh mih madan u rangap kol kynsai kane ka klob, u Subrata Paul uba don hapdeng ka kynrum kynram hadien ka jingbna ba u pyndonkam dawai khleh drok. Jowai, Jymmang 10: U General Secretary ka West Jaiñtia Jaiñtia District Sports Association (WJDSA) u ma Lammat OO Laloo, ula pyntip ba ka ïew kyntiap klob (inter club transfer) jong ka wat kaba nyngkong (first window transfer) kala poi noh sha kaba kut mynta ka nohphaisngi.

U ma Lammat OO Laloo, ula ong ba ki don haduh 55 ngut ki player phutbol kiba la mih naka klob barim bad pynïasoh sha ki klob ba thymmai haka kyrdan Under-16 haduh Super Division ka WJDSA.

Ha shuwa ban kut ka ïew kyntiap klob ki don haduh 11 ngut ki player phutbol kila wan shakhmat ban soi register Inter District Transfer ban sdang ïalehkai ha ki klob thymmai mynta ka aiom ha sor Shillong, Amlarem, Sutnga bad Laskeiñ

Ka Wahingdoh, ka klob na sor Shillong kala pynrung haduh saw ngut ki rang ïalehkai ba kynthup ïa u Deiwomsade Kyndait, uba ju ïalehkai naka Sohmynting, Brightness star Lynthong, uba ju ïalehkai na ka Seng Derew War, Marbiangki Suchiang uba na Ladthadlaboh bad u Georgeki Phrangki Ryngkhlem, uba na Shangpung. Katba ki hynriew ngut kiwei pat ki player kin ïalehkai bad ki klob ba thymmai ha Amlarem, Sutnga bad ka Laskeiñ. Ka jingpynkheiñ aiñ ki nongniah kali ha kylleng ka jylla Meghalaya katba nang mih ki sngi ka la nang kiew manla ka sngi namar ka jingdon ïa ka mynsiem sarong bad sngew hangamei kaba la kiew haduh shynrong khlieh khlem da suidniew shuh ïa ki aiñ ki kyndon ba ka Sorkar ka pynjari khnang ban ïada ïa ki paidbah nongniah kali bad ïa ki nongleit nongwan ba kiba ïaid lynti ha surok khnang ban tem ïa ka jingmynsaw bad ka jingduhei ki mynsiem bakordor ha ka khyllipmat bym poi pyrkhat.

Katkum ka jingïoh jingkheiñ tang haduh u bnai Ïaiong, 2017 la lap ba ki don haduh 120 ngut ki briew kiba la duhei ïa ka jingim na kine ki jingjia aksiden ha ki rukom jingjia bapher bapher.

Lah ban kdew, dang shen ha ka 26 tarik, Rymphang mynta u snem kumba 17 ngut ki briew ki la duhei ïa ka jingim bad 60 ngut tam eiei kiwei pat ki la mynsaw jur ha ka jingaksiden kali ha Jaidoh Khroh, West Khasi Hills District katba ki dang thmu ban leit ïashim bynta ha ka jingïaseng jong ka KJP Synod ha ka shnong Nonglang tang namarba u nongniah jong kane ka kali u la pynher stet shaba palat ïa ka kali kat haduh ba ka la wanrah pat ka jingsngewsih ïa ki bahaing hasem kiba la duhnoh khlem dei por ïa la ki baieid bathoiñ.

Na ka liang ka tnat pynïaid kali ka nongbah Shillong ka pynpaw ba ki daw tynrai kiba wanrah ïa ki jingjia aksident ha ka jylla ka dei na ka daw ka jingniah khlemakor hi ki nongniah kali bad ka jingniah kali khlem pyrkhat shuh kat haduh ba la shu pynher ïa ka kali kumba niah liengsuiñ.

Kiwei kiwei ki daw jong ki jingjia aksident ha ka kylleng ka nongbah Shllong ka dei ruh ka jingniah kali jong ki khynnah samla kiba shu niah kali shongshit khlem tip ïa ki kyndon aiñ niah kali jong ka Motor Vehicle Act.

Kaba pyndiaw ïa ka tnat Pulit ka long wat hapdeng ki jingtrei shitom ban pynlong ïa ki jingai jinghikai bapher bapher ha kylleng ki shnong bad ki district pynban ki nongniah kali ki dang leh matlah ïa ki aiñ bad ïa ki kyndon niah kali.

Ka jingtehlakam ka tnat pynïaid kali jong ki Pulit ban mana pyndonkam ïa ka Mobile Phone ha ka por ba niah kali, ka treikam tang haba ki nongniah kali ki ïohi ba don u Pulit Traffic hynrei kim salia ban kren mobile phone sahuh bad la ka niah kali ba kit ïa ki nongleit jingleit ha ryngkat ka pynher kali kaba wanrah ym tang ïa ki jingjia basngewsih hynrei kaba wanrah ruh ïa ka dheng kali khamtam ha sor Shillong kaba bun bha ki kali ba ïaid baroh arphew saw kynta nalor ka surok ka long kaba rit bad khapngiah khamtam ha ka por long skul bad long trei.

Wat hapdeng kine ki jingtrei shitom ka Shillong Traffic Police ban pynsngewthuh ïa ki nongniah kali ha nongbah Shillong ïa ki kyndon bad ki aiñ niah kali, hynrei watla katta ki dang don ki nongpynkheiñ aiñ namar katkum ka jingai jingkheiñ mynta u snem 2017 tang naduh u bnai Kyllalyngkot haduh Ïaiong ki nongniah kali ba pynkheiñ aiñ ki don haduh 6, 948 hajar ngut.

Katkum ka jingïoh lum jingkheiñ na Shillong Traffic Police ha u bnai Kyllalyngkot, 2017 ki nongniah kali ba pynkheiñ ki don haduh 1,830 ngut, ha u Rymphang, 1,976 ngut, ha u Lber 1,564 ngut bad ha u bnai Ïaiong ki don haduh 1,578 ngut.

Na kine ki 6,948 hajar ngut ki nongpynkheiñ aiñ ka tnat Pulit ka la ïoh lum ïa ka kuna haduh T. 24, 88,330 lak.

Kane ka jingïoh lum jingkheiñ ki pulit, ka pynpaw shuh shuh ba ki nongniah kali ba pynieng ha ki jaka No Parking ki don haduh 1,820 tylli, bud sa ki nongniah kali bym ju deng Seat Belt kiba don haduh 1,473 ngut.

Ka jingdon ki nongniah kali ba ïaid sha ki surok No Entry ha kylleng ka nongbah Shillong ki don haduh 586 ngut, 511 ki dei ki nongniah kali ba pynwit ïa ka surok bad 289 ngut kiba la dih kyiad ha ka por niah kali.

Wat hadien ba la mana tyngeh ban tah plastik iong ïa ki kali hynrei ki pulit ki la ïohkem haduh 188 ngut kiba la pynkheiñ ïa kane ka jingmana.

Ki pulit ki la ïoh kem ruh haduh 341 ngut ki nongniah kali bym don Driving Licence bad 164 ngut ki nongniah kali ki bym don ïa ki kot ki sla kali.

Kane ka jingïoh lum jingkheiñ na ki pulit ka ïathuh ruh ba ki don 197 ngut ki nongniah thuk thuk khlem ka Helmet bad 74 ngut ki nongniah kali ba kren Mobile Phone ha ka por niah kali.

Ka jingkiew ki jingjia aksiden kali naduh u Kyllalyngkot haduh Ïaiong, 2017 katkum ka jingïoh lum jingkheiñ ki pulit ka long haduh 123 tylli bad 45 tylli ki jingjia aksiden na ka jingniah kali khlem akor ki nongniah kali.

Ki pulit pynïaid kali ki la ïoh shaiñ kuna ruh haduh 141 ngut ki nongniah kali kamai ba kit palat pud.

La sngewdei ban ai jingïaroh ïa ka tnat Pynïaid Kali khamtam ïa u Bah Nangkiew K. Syiem, SP (Traffic) uba ju shim ïa ki lad ki lynti ban pyllait ïa ka jingdheng kali ha nongbah Shillong bad kumjuh ruh ban pdiang ïa ki jingai jingmut na ki riewpaidbah kumno ban pynduna ïa ka jingaksiden ki kali bad kumjuh ruh ban weng ïa ka dheng kali ha nongbah Shillong khnang ban pynsuk ïa ki paidbah nongleit nongwan. Ka ilekshon 2018 kam da shim por shuh hapoh kane ka Jylla jong ngi, kum ki paitbah ngi don ka por sa katto katne bnai ban ïohi ïa ki nongsynshar kiba thymmai ïa ki san snem ki ban wan. Haba ka samoi ilekshon ka la jan ngi ïohi ha ki kot khubor ba man la ka sngi ka la don ka jingïa kawang ktieh hapdeng ki political party kiba pher kiba pher. Kane ka jingïakawang ktieh ka la jia ym tang hapdeng ki National Party kum ka BJP bad ka Congress hynrei ngi ïohi ruh ba wat ki party riewlum ruh ki la ïa shim bynta shitrhem ha kane ka jingïakawang ktieh. Kawei pa ka wei ka party ka don la ka jong ka thong bad kata ka long ban bat ïa ka bor synshar hapoh ka jylla. Haba nga peit bniah ha ki kot khubor ba man la ka sngi. Nga ïohi ba don kiba ong bad sngew ba ki party riewlum imat kin don ka jingïasngewthuh jingmut hapdeng jong ki ban ïa synrop lang bad ban bat ïa ka bor synshar ha u snem 2018. Kane ka dei tang ka jingïohi jong ki riew saiñ pyrthei bad ki kato katne kiba khmihlynti ba kan urlong. Hynrei haba ngi phai dien ha kine ki khyndiat snem ba la lah ngim ïohi satïa ïa ka jingïalong ka wei hapdeng ki Party riewlum wat tang ha District Council. Ka jingïabishni ka jingïapihuiñ hapdeng ki party riewlum ka la paw pyrthei kiba ngi kum ki paitbah ki la ïohi lut. Kane ka dei ka nuksa kaba rit kaba nga kwah ban pynpaw sha phi ki paitbah ka bri u hynniew trep hynñiew skum. Lada tang ha Discrict Council kim lah ban ïa tylli lang ka wei ka lah mo ban ïa long lang ka wei hapoh Iing dorbar thawaiñ. Balei kaba kum kane ka wan jia hapdeng ki seng riewlum? Bad ka jubab kaba shai hi ka long ima