Haba ngi phai sha ka BJP kawei na ki seng saiñ pyrthei kaba la suh thied bha mynta hapoh ri India hi baroh kawei. Ka la sdang ban suhthied wat ha kane ka jylla jong ngi lyngba ki nongïalam kiba tbit jong kane ka party. Kane ka party ruh hapoh ka jylla ka la pynnoh mynsiem ïa ki katto katne ki riew ngeit khristan da kaba pynlong ïa ka GOOD GOVERNANCE DAY ha ka sngi Khristmas bad ïa ka DIGITAL INDIA DAY ha ka sngi GOOD Friday. Ki paidriewngeit Khristan wat la ki la sngew pyrshah ïa kine ki sngi hynrei ka jingshisha ki long ba kine baroh ar tyllli ki sngi kim shym la ktah ei ei ïa ki Khristan kiba da duwai shisha, kiba da mane Blei shisha bad kam shim la ktah ïa ka leit ka wan jingïaseng ha kine ki sngi. Kane kan nym ktah da lei lei ruh em ïa ki Khristan kiba da pynshong nongrim ha ka jingngeit jong ki, kiba skhem ka jingngeit bad kiba bud shisha ïa ki jinghikai shong tynrai jong ka Baibl. Ka jingsynshar ka BJP kum ha Goa kaba u pait nongshong shnong hi kiba bun ki dei ki Khristan. Ka BJP ka la pynshai paitbah ruh lyngba u nongïalam jong ka u Himanta Biswa Sarma ba ka 25 tarik u bnai December kaba dei ka sngi Khristmas ka shu ïa tyngkhuh bad ka sngikha u PM barim jong ka NDA u Shri. Atal Behari Vajpayee bad ka Digital India Day kaba dei ka Good Friday ka ïa tyngkhuh bad ka sngikha jong u B.R.Ambedkar kaba la long ha ka 14 tarik u Iaïong 2017 bad kane ka ïai kylla man la u snem. Ha une u snem 2018 kan hap ha ka 29 tarik u bnai March. Kane kam dei ka jingleh khnang ban pynsngew sih ïa ki pait riew ngeit Khristan hynrei tang ka jingrakhie pyndon burom ïa ki riew khraw jong kane ka ri. Nangta ka don shuh shuh sa kawei ka daw kaba la kynnoh pyrshah ïa kane ka party kum kawei ka party kaba pyrshah ban shoh ne bam doh masi. Kane lehse kan jia tang ïa kito ki niam kiba pyrshah ban bam ïa ka doh masi kum ka niam Hindu hynrei ym ïa kiwei pat ki jait niam ki bym pyrshah ha kaba bam doh masi. Ngi ïohi kum ha ka jylla Uttar Pradesh la khang pyrshah ïa kito kiba leh beaiñ ha kaba sh